instance virtual_to_physical_interaction : DTDFVocab:VirtualToPhysical [
    base:desc "The DT controller consumes RabbitMQ messages and publishes command messages (heatbed on/off, fan on/off, desired setpoint) that the low‑level driver translates into GPIO signals and MOSFET actuator control on the Raspberry Pi."
